page1.title: About Me
page1.content: . I am a dedicated, hardworking and proactive individual who passionate and has excellent technical skills in computer networking, data science, machine learning, and other IT technologies. I have solid experiences in campus organizations, enabling me to develop my interpersonal and managerial skills. I am currently looking for an opportunity to utilise my technical skills in a challenging working environment and become a valuable asset to the organisation that I work for. . Education . Institut Teknologi Sepuluh Nopember – Electrical Engineering (Telecommunication) . GPA 3.44/4.0 | Graduated with Microstrip Antenna Design for Final Thesis | 3 Month Intership at PT. Telkom Akses as Fiber Optic Engineer | . Organization Experience . Antenna & Propagation Laboratory ITS . Became a laboratory assistant focusing on study of antennas, radios, and other telecommunication technologies. | Organized practical laboratory work, educated younger students, and helped lecturers researches, such as microstrip antenna and matlab projects. | . Himpunan Mahasiswa Teknik Elektro ITS . Actively contributed to faculty events, trainings, and discussion forums, learnt and implemented managerial and organizational skills. | Responsible for coordinating and helping 8 younger students in their student orientation to adapt to campus life. | . Skills . Networking (CCNA), Programming (Python, Matlab, C++), Data Science, Machine Learning (Scikit-learn), Deep Learning (Tensorflow, PyTorch), SQL, Tableau, AWS, Git, Operating Systems (Windows, Linux), Intermediate English, Microsoft Office, Statistics | .
